IPSComponent, Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable, Collection, List, RandomAccess
public class PSAaRelationshipList
extends PSCollectionComponent

A collection of PSAaRelationship objects. See PSXAaRelationshipList.dtd. The sort rank of the each relationship is implicit in that the order of appearance in the list is assumed to the sort rank.
